## [Unreleased]
### Changed
- Migrate to CRD based cluster API stack

### Added
- Allow to specify availability zone in placement
- Support for machine classes
- Record machine events

## [0.1.0] - 2018-10-17
### Added

- Self-standing binary allows tp bootstrap Kubernetes cluster with cluster API stack deployed
- Requeue failed machines every 20s until running
- Security groups and subnets can be specified via filters
- AMI can be looked up by specifing filters
- Actuator can be run as self-standing binary (with create, exists and delete operations)

